{"title":"相望","authors":["杨爱伦"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":1,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"相望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨爱伦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个迷人的夜晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖水轻拍着堤岸；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们深情地彼此凝望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此我的心里有了一个太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象两片飘零的柳叶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象两朵追逐的白云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象青藤缠绵着大树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深渊里叠印着子夜的月光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许天涯海角，人各一方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许连名字都已遗忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要想起那深情的凝望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的心里就升起太阳。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}